## ERROR TIPS

### Full Inventory Warnings
- Ensure that chests are regularly emptied to prevent mining and smelting operations from halting due to full inventories.

### Blocked Drop Positions
- Verify that inserters have clear drop positions to maintain efficient item transfer from furnaces to storage.

### Furnace Output Full
- Regularly transfer items from furnace outputs to prevent production stoppages due to full output inventories.
